				<p>Tried this today and it was my first ever utter failure at baking.  The pudding did. not. set.  I know you were not here in my kitchen so you probably can&#8217;t tell me what i did wrong, but any more specifics you can give about thickening up the pudding?  How long is it on the stove?  How briskly do you whisk it on the stove? How thick is thick?  Does it get thick like Jello pudding on the stove?  </p>
